Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Can easily be used as a two tenant building
Parking lot new in 2019. Roof new in 2014. Turn key interior.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Two-level renovated office property is ideal for an owner-user as the current owner is vacating at the end of June 2020. Built on a slope, each level has an entrance and separate parking lot. Entire building was renovated in 2018 with beautiful finishes and updated conference rooms, training room, outdoor patio, break rooms and new bathrooms.  Site is 6.65 acres in the very low vacancy market of Genesee Business Park. Seller has spent ~$600,000 on interior renovations, new parking lot, HVAC in the past two years. Don't miss this wonderful opportunity in the West sub-market of Denver.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 18,904 SF Vacant Office Building in Low Vacancy Genesee Trail Business Park
